---
title: Nan's Rump Steak & Roast Veggie Toss with Caramelised Onion Chutney & Garlic Aioli
description: This heavenly rump steak coated in Nan’s special seasoning is full of flavour, thanks to paprika, pepper, onion and garlic.
Add a medley of veggies, crunchy flaked almonds and a dollop of our garlic aioli and it’s satisfaction, guaranteed!
